{"tid":848574,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"再見美國隊長","createTime":"2018-10-05T04:38:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T09:56:28.000Z","uid":105567,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"334303f432923b56bdd4ca774efcbfcf305e3428","tid":848574,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T04:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/123726_0067340462135b93abaedcf0b99253c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2F123726_0067340462135b93abaedcf0b99253c6.jpg&h=ecca5003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飾演美國隊長（Captain America）的克里斯˙伊凡斯（Chris Evans）已經完成了自己在《復仇者聯盟4（暫）》劇組裡的任務。<br />\n<br />\n今天稍早，克里斯在Twitter感性地寫下：<br />\n<br />\n「《復仇者聯盟4（暫）》正式殺青。這可以說是令人百感交集的一天。在過去8年來，扮演這名角色一直都是我的榮幸。對每一位身在幕前、幕後、以及觀眾席的各位，謝謝你們為我帶來了這些回憶，我會永遠心懷感謝。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然這番話語被普遍解讀為某種形式的「告別」，但就像過往幾次引發外界熱議的報導一樣，克里斯在推文裡其實並沒有明確指出自己與Marvel Studios之間的合作關係已經劃下句點，因此美國隊長這名角色將會在《復仇者聯盟4（暫）》裡面臨怎樣的命運、往後觀眾又是否能繼續在本系列作品裡看到克里斯的身影，一切都仍有待我們的親眼見證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ChrisEvans/status/1047896966410190849\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FChrisEvans%2Fstatus%2F1047896966410190849&d=%2FrE3f8HXw7%2BNXC4UwzoGVgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=263583c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FChrisEvans%2Fstatus%2F1047896966410190849&h=0c030a87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ChrisEvans/status/1047896966410190849</a>"},{"pid":"604b44a1461549b5233084a6f925931dc66e1bef","tid":848574,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T04:52:46.000Z","msg":"希望唔會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1019ce5ffea1d2cf79631c69486f68a22ede20e","tid":848574,"uid":186784,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"604b44a1461549b5233084a6f925931dc66e1bef","tid":848574,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,